----TO RUN THIS----
1. Download and run Ollama locally - Gemma3:1b
2. Download home.html and server.js files into empty directory
3. Open command prompt:
	- cd {directory of folder}
	- npm init -y
	- npm install express cors node-fetch
	- node server.js
(this should have created package.json/package-lock.json files in folder. node server.js should display 'backend running at http://localhost:3000')
4. Open html file in folder to run
5. Enter topic into text box
6. Click generate
